### Aegis flights API
### Run with REST Client extension. Replace cookie after sign-in.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=...replace_after_signin...
@personId = REPLACE_WITH_ARTIST_OR_CREW_ID

### List
GET {{host}}/api/flights
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List filtered: arrivals only
GET {{host}}/api/flights?direction=inbound
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List filtered: by person
GET {{host}}/api/flights?personKind=artist&personId={{personId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Search by flight number / airline / airport / PNR
GET {{host}}/api/flights?search=ME202
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create — success
# @name createFlight
POST {{host}}/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "personKind": "artist",
  "personId": "{{personId}}",
  "direction": "inbound",
  "fromAirport": "CDG",
  "toAirport": "BEY",
  "airline": "MEA",
  "flightNumber": "ME202",
  "scheduledDt": "2026-08-13T14:30:00Z",
  "status": "scheduled",
  "pnr": "ABC123",
  "seat": "14A"
}

### Create — failure: bad direction
POST {{host}}/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "personKind": "artist",
  "personId": "{{personId}}",
  "direction": "sideways"
}

### Create — failure: bad URL
POST {{host}}/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "personKind": "artist",
  "personId": "{{personId}}",
  "direction": "inbound",
  "ticketUrl": "not a url"
}

### Get one
@flightId = REPLACE_WITH_FLIGHT_ID
GET {{host}}/api/flights/{{flightId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Patch — partial: just mark landed
PATCH {{host}}/api/flights/{{flightId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "status": "landed" }

### Patch — clear actualDt
PATCH {{host}}/api/flights/{{flightId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "actualDt": "" }

### Patch — empty body (400)
PATCH {{host}}/api/flights/{{flightId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{}

### Delete
DELETE {{host}}/api/flights/{{flightId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}
